20:49.160 --> 20:51.754
Five. Five grand.

20:55.360 --> 20:57.396
Five grand.

20:58.040 --> 21:01.953
That's good. Now find them.
But don't touch, they're mine.

21:02.040 --> 21:03.996
I'm gonna teach these guys a lesson.

21:04.080 --> 21:06.150
Goddamn it, D'Salvio.

21:06.960 --> 21:11.272
